              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Today we buy finished plastic legs from a city factory for $344 a bed. The recycled plastic inside is worth about $40. We are paying $300 for someone else to press it. Press our own legs on Country and a set costs about $150. That single change saves $194 on every bed.",
