              "id": "e8AHy",
              "name": "T",
              "fill": "$ink",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "This quarter the work went home. Young people in Alice Springs built the beds, kept the first ones they made, and 107 went out to the homelands with Oonchiumpa. The federal REAL Innovation Fund decision is expected within weeks. If it lands, the build crew becomes a paid local workforce, and the on-Country plant moves from commissioning toward community ownership.",
              "lineHeight": 1.45,
              "fontFamily": "$body",
              "fontSize": 17,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
